# Product Sales Analysis I

## Problem Type
Basic INNER JOIN

## What I Learned

- INNER JOIN returns only matching rows.
- Used to combine information from Product and Sales tables.
- Matching key was product_id.

## Pattern

Need only matching records from both tables.

Use:
INNER JOIN

## Difficulty

Easy

## Solution

```mysql
SELECT P.product_name,
       S.year,
       S.price
FROM Sales S
INNER JOIN Product P
ON S.product_id = P.product_id;
```
